! HTTP + DNS config

ip http server
ip http session-module-list http-module-list SCEP
ip http client source-interface GigabitEthernet2
ip http secure-server

ip dns view vrf 101 VOICE
 domain name-server vrf 101 10.15.{{ node_number }}.1
 dns forwarder vrf 101 10.15.{{ node_number }}.1
 dns forwarding source-interface GigabitEthernet2.101

ip dns view-list VOICE
 view vrf 101 VOICE 1

ip dns server view-group VOICE
ip dns server